{
  "text": "• For DMR, we evaluate the three cases (interpolation, prediction and motion deblur) described in Fig. 2 on the DAVIS dataset [CITATION_1] , and compare against state-ofthe-art event-based algorithms, i.e., Complementary Filter [CITATION_2] and Event-based Double Integral [CITATION_3] . • For RD, we first discuss how to use the trained RD.",
